ISLAMABAD, Apr 2 (APP): Prime Minister Imran Khan Saturday asked all members of the provincial assembly in Punjab to ensure they vote for Chaudhry Pervez Elahi for the election of Chief Minister.
In a tweet on social media platform Twitter, he said, “All PTI MPAs in Punjab must ensure they vote for Ch Pervez Elahi in the CM Punjab election tomorrow. Any PTI MPA going against party direction, including abstaining from vote, will be disqualified and will face strict disciplinary action.”
